===============================================
opmode,id,valuetype,entityid,subproperties,unitcode,datasetid,geopoint,observedat
Create,location,GeoPoint,urn:ngsi-ld:entities:E1,f,,None,01010000A0E6100000000000000000F03F00000000000000400000000000000840,


04. See the sub-attributes in the temporal database
===================================================
id,valuetype,entityid,attrinstanceid,unitcode,text,number,boolean,observedat


